The Federation has 30 member Societies and 4 associated Societies, representing over 6,000 parasitologists, all over Europe. &#xd;
&#xd;
&#xd;
Each society have to pay a 0.5 € fee for each of its active members per year. The funds should be sent to the Banca Nazionale del Lavoro, Naples, Italy. Most of the EFP funds are used to grant students to attend the EMOPs and to award Young Scientists every 4 years (see www.eurofedpar.eu).&#xd;
